	Scarlett woes    
	 Los Angeles, Dec. 22 (PTI): They had announced that they are ending their marriage with love and kindness. However, according to reports, Ryan Reynolds feels that Scarlett Johansson treated him badly.       
	Reynolds was open about his marital woes on the sets of The Green Lantern, reports Us magazine. He said she treated him badly. It never seemed like she made him a priority, said a source close to Reynolds. The source added that while the 34-year-old actor is beyond sad and depressed about the split, Johansson is disconnected and disaffected.     
	Paris scare    
	Los Angeles (PTI): Reality TV star Paris Hilton was evacuated from her plane on Wednesday after a fellow traveller discovered a four-inch serrated knife hidden in a pocket on the plane. The socialite was heading to Maui for a break when the plane was evacuated by security at Los Angeles airport. We were about to take off then security made everyone deplane because they found a big knife on board the plane. Scary that it got on plane, tweeted Hilton.
                                                                                                                                                      
